<div xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" type="讀誦" xml:id="gsz0871b17shiShouZhen"><lb
ed="T" n="0871b17"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0871b17"/><head><date from-iso="+0960-02-09" key="j20717322132856" to-iso="+1127-06-18"><anchor xml:id="beg0871004"/>宋<anchor xml:id="end0871004"/></date><placeName key="PL000000023413"><placeName>東京</placeName><placeName>開寶寺</placeName></placeName><persName key="A013628">守真</persName>傳（<persName key="A013633">沙彌彌伽</persName> <persName key="A013634">道蔭</persName>）</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0871b18"/><persName key="A013628">釋守真</persName>，<placeName key="PL000000042206"><placeName>永興</placeName><placeName>萬年</placeName></placeName>人也。俗姓<name>紀</name><ptr target="#n3142"/>，<placeName key="PL000000000097">漢</placeName>詐帝<ptr target="#n3141"/><persName key="A018052">信</persName>之<lb
ed="T" n="0871b19"/>鴻緒<ptr type="glossary" target="#g2041"/>。乃祖乃父，素履貞吉<ptr type="glossary" target="#g2042"/>，<anchor xml:id="beg0871sgsz10"/>奕<anchor xml:id="end0871sgsz10"/>葉<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1505"/>孝行，充塞閭<lb
ed="T" n="0871b20"/>里，故鄉人美其孝焉，遂目之曰<persName>紀丁蘭</persName>也<ptr target="#n3144"/>──<lb
ed="T" n="0871b21"/><persName key="A013628">真</persName>即其後矣！洎<persName key="A008599">黃</persName>寇<anchor xml:id="beg0871sgsz12"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>于</sic><corr>干</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0871sgsz12"/>紀，<persName key="A005228">僖宗</persName>蒙塵，車駕避<lb
ed="T" n="0871b22"/>鋒而西幸<ptr target="#n981"/>，<placeName key="PL000000043060">咸</placeName>、<placeName key="PL000000042189">鎬</placeName>失守而沒賊，因而徙家居<lb
ed="T" n="0871b23"/>于<placeName key="PL000000034805">蜀</placeName>矣<ptr target="#n3143"/>。及<date key="j20545712054924" from-iso="+0913-02-14" to-iso="+0914-02-02">冠</date>也，偶遊<placeName key="PL000000034692">聖壽寺</placeName>見<persName key="A013629">修進<roleName>律師</roleName></persName><lb
ed="T" n="0871b24"/>行出物表，語越常度，乃解帶卸冠，北面而<lb
ed="T" n="0871b25"/>事之。七支<ptr type="glossary" target="#g2043"/>既備，先謁<persName key="A013631">從朗<roleName>師</roleName></persName>，學《起信論》<ptr target="#n1108"/>；次<lb
ed="T" n="0871b26"/>依<persName key="A013632">性光<roleName>師</roleName></persName>，傳法界觀<ptr target="#n1296"/>；後<anchor xml:id="beg0871sgsz14"/>禮<anchor xml:id="end0871sgsz14"/><persName key="A024585">演祕<roleName>闍梨</roleName></persName>，授瑜<lb
ed="T" n="0871b27"/>伽教，竝得心要，咸盡指歸。自明達諸法，<lb
ed="T" n="0871b28"/>宣暢妙典，四十年間略無怠矣。而賜號曰<lb
ed="T" n="0871b29"/><persName key="A013628">昭信</persName>焉。講《起信》及法界觀共七十餘遍，皆<pb ed="T" n="0871c" xml:id="T50.2061.0871c"/><lb
ed="T" n="0871c01"/>以燈傳燈，用器投器<ptr type="glossary" target="#g2045"/>，嗣乎法者二十許人。<lb
ed="T" n="0871c02"/>開灌頂<ptr type="glossary" target="#g97"/>道場五遍，約度僧尼士庶三千餘<lb
ed="T" n="0871c03"/>人，開水陸道場二十遍。常五更輪，結<persName key="A002144">文殊</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0871c04"/>五髻教法，至夜二更輪，西方無量壽教法<ptr target="#n3145"/>，<lb
ed="T" n="0871c05"/>稱<persName key="A002843">阿彌陀</persName>尊號，修念佛三昧，期生淨域。一<lb
ed="T" n="0871c06"/>日，謂弟子<persName key="A024586">緣遇</persName>曰：「<persName key="A002799">如來</persName>不云『出息不保入<lb
ed="T" n="0871c07"/>息』<ptr target="#n3146"/>？<ref type="person" target="#A013628">吾</ref>之壽也幸矣，<ref type="person" target="#A024586">汝</ref>之年也耄<ptr type="glossary" target="#g2044"/>矣，今欲順<lb
ed="T" n="0871c08"/>俗從世，預設二塔，其可得乎？」<persName key="A024586">緣遇</persName>稽首而<lb
ed="T" n="0871c09"/>對曰：「<persName key="A024587">廣度<roleName>長老</roleName></persName>捨院之右地請建塔者有<lb
ed="T" n="0871c10"/>年矣！今<ref type="person" target="#A013628">大師</ref>屬其意，<ref type="person" target="#A024587">長老</ref>致其美，因緣冥<lb
ed="T" n="0871c11"/>契，安可而止。」於是鳩工而營之，自十月琢<lb
ed="T" n="0871c12"/>磨，至<anchor xml:id="beg0871005"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>來</sic><corr>十</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0871005"/>一月徹<anchor xml:id="beg0871sgsz16"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>繢</sic><corr>績</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0871sgsz16"/><ptr type="glossary" target="#g794"/>。以<date key="j20759592075959" when-iso="+0971-09-06"><name>開寶</name>四年秋八月九<lb
ed="T" n="0871c13"/>日</date><ptr target="#n3147"/>命眾念佛，佛聲既久，令止，奄然而歸寂，<lb
ed="T" n="0871c14"/>俗壽七十八，僧臘五十三。<date key="j20759712075971" when-iso="+0971-09-18">其月二十一日</date>焚<lb
ed="T" n="0871c15"/>葬於北<placeName key="PL000000055458">永泰門</placeName>外<placeName key="PL000000055453">智度院</placeName>側。其獲舍利光潤，<lb
ed="T" n="0871c16"/>各將供養之。次沙彌<persName key="A013633">彌伽</persName>者，<placeName key="PL000000047983">于闐國</placeName>人也<ptr target="#n3148"/>，專<lb
ed="T" n="0871c17"/>誦《華嚴經》，曾無間息。<date key="j19759911976879" notAfter-iso="+0700-05-30" notBefore-iso="+0697-12-23"><name>聖曆</name>年中</date>，<persName key="A002869">天帝釋</persName>請迎<lb
ed="T" n="0871c18"/><persName key="A013633">伽</persName>上天誦持，乃曰：「每被<persName key="A008593">阿脩羅</persName>見擾，故屈<lb
ed="T" n="0871c19"/><ref type="person" target="#A013633">師</ref>來，請為誦宣《華嚴經》，以禳彼敵。」遂陞座，<lb
ed="T" n="0871c20"/>朗諷是經。時<persName key="A008593">修羅</persName>軍眾聞經乃現威神，一<lb
ed="T" n="0871c21"/>時而化去<ptr target="#n3149"/>。又沙彌<persName key="A013634">道蔭</persName><ptr target="#n3150"/>常念《金剛經》，<date key="j20224182022595" notAfter-iso="+0825-07-29" notBefore-iso="+0825-02-02"><name>寶曆</name>初</date><ptr target="#n698"/>，<lb
ed="T" n="0871c22"/>因他出夜歸，虎暴中路，忽遇哮吼跳躑于<lb
ed="T" n="0871c23"/>前。<persName key="A013634">蔭</persName>知不免，乃閉目而坐，唯默念是經，心<lb
ed="T" n="0871c24"/>期救護，虎遂伏草守之。達曙，村人來往，乃<lb
ed="T" n="0871c25"/>視虎，其蹲處涎流於地焉。<persName key="A013634">蔭</persName>後持誦，益加<lb
ed="T" n="0871c26"/>高行矣。</p><milestone unit="page" rend="pagebreak"/>
